When it comes to analyzing customer feedback and answering question like 'Is the measured NPS of one customer group higher than another' you can call your market research provider, use paid DIY-solutions or familiarize with your choice of open-source packages that enables you to automate boring stuff. 

The value of customer feedback

Deliver valuable increments and maximize the value of your product is essential in Scrum. As value comes in many different forms as a Product Owner you have to find the right balance between different measures for internal and external value.

